  "Down a group": "",
  "Up a group": "",
  "Across a period": "",
  "Diagonally": "",
  "Going down a group adds entire electron shells (1s → 1s,2s,2p → etc.). Each added shell provides an additional layer of shielding for valence electrons. Li has 2 core e⁻; Cs has 54.": "",
