  "Less shielding effect": "",
  "No shielding": "",
  "Greater shielding effect": "",
  "More nuclear charge": "",
  "Each electron shell acts as a barrier. More shells = more barriers = more shielding. This is why atoms get larger and ionization energy decreases going down a group.": "",
