  "They are equal": "",
  "Li (fewer electron shells)": "",
  "Neither has shielding": "",
  "Cs (more electron shells)": "",
  "Cs has 6 shells (54 core electrons shielding the 6s¹ valence electron), while Li has only 2 shells (2 core electrons shielding the 2s¹). Cs has far more shielding.": "",
